{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_06_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 3話 アイドルとして",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ダンス大会当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the dance competition",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "会場入りしたが、異様な雰囲気だな\nみんな怜を遠巻きに見るだけで、誰も近づいて来ないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The atmosphere seems strange as soon as I entered the competition venue.\nEveryone is staring at Rei from a distance‚ but nobody's approaching her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私の出場はネットでも話題になっていましたから\n疎ましく感じてるんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My participation has become a hot topic online‚\nso it seems they're feeling a bit alienated.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ダンサーの立場なら、自分達のステージに\nアイドルがしゃしゃり出て、いい気はしませんよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From a dancer's perspective‚\nhaving an idol suddenly take center stage might be upsetting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜にとっては完全にアウェーってことか……\nだが、中には怜と話したい人もいるみたいだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Rei is completely an outsider here…\nHowever‚ it seems there are a few who do want to engage in a conversation with Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.333333399997,
          "startTime": 33.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ……エリカ……\n向こうも準備は出来ているみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Ah… Erika…\nIt seems she's also prepared on her end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-hiraeri001.m4a",
      "text": "怜……よく恥ずかしげもなく顔を出せたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei… You have the audacity to show your face here‚ shamelessly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "今日は決着をつけに来たわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came here today to settle things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-hiraeri002.m4a",
      "text": "ふざけないで。そんなヒラヒラしたドレスで踊る気？\n自分が場違いだって分からないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't make me laugh. You plan to dance in that pretty dress?\nDon't you realize you don't belong here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-hiraeri003.m4a",
      "text": "そもそもダンスから逃げてアイドルになったあんたが\n今更大会に出たところで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You‚ who ran away from dancing to become an idol‚\nnow suddenly appear in this competition…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "それは違うわ。私はダンスから逃げた訳じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. I didn't run away from dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "私のダンスを生かす道を考えて\nアイドルに可能性を見出しただけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just considered a path where I could express my dance\nand found potential in being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "私はダンスを捨てていない\n今日、あなたに勝ってそれを証明するわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never abandoned dancing.\nI will prove it by defeating you today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Erika",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-hiraeri004.m4a",
      "text": "真剣にダンス一筋に打ち込んできた私が\nアイドルに負ける訳ないでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way I‚ who have dedicated myself solely to dancing‚\nwould lose to an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "いくら口で言っても納得しないでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter what I say‚ you won't be convinced.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "だからパフォーマンスで、あなたが馬鹿にした\n『アイドル』の本気を思い知らせてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ through my performance‚\nI'll show you the sincerity of the \"idol\" you've been belittling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 98.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 98.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（プログラムが順調に進んで、いよいよ怜の出番だが）\n（果たしてアイドルが受け入れてもらえるのか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The program is going smoothly‚ and it's finally Rei's turn.)\n(I wonder if they will accept an idol here…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 107.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "会場のみなさん、こんにちは！\nエントリーナンバー12番、一ノ瀬怜です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ everyone in the venue!\nI'm entry number 12‚ Ichinose Rei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 115.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "今日、私はアイドルとしてここに来ました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I came here as an idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 119.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（会場がざわついているな……。ダンス大会なのに）\n（いきなりアイドル宣言されたら困惑するのも当然か）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(There's a buzz in the venue… It's a dance competition after all.)\n(Isn't it natural to be confused if someone suddenly declares I'm an idol?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 119.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 127.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "世の中にはいろんなダンスがあります\nどんなダンスも等しく素敵で素晴らしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are many types of dances in the world.\nEvery dance is equally wonderful and magnificent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "私の……アイドルのダンスを見てそれを感じて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please watch my idol dance and feel that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 141.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "ここからはアイドルが輝く時間です！\nテンション上げて行きますよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ it's time for the idol to shine!\nLet's raise the tension and get going!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（サニピの曲にあわせて笑顔で明るく元気に踊って……）\n（怜はあくまでアイドルとして勝つつもりだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She dances energetically with a bright smile to Sunny Peace's song…)\n(Rei is determined to win as an idol.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
